      "message": "Implement retry behavior 2.1, opt-in via `AWS_NEW_RETRIES_2026=true` environment variable. Non-throttling errors now use 50ms base backoff (previously 1,000ms). Transient retry quota cost is 14 tokens (previously 5). DynamoDB and DynamoDB Streams use a 25ms base backoff and increase default max attempts to 4 (from 3). Long-polling operations (SQS `ReceiveMessage`, SFN `GetActivityTask`, SWF `PollForActivityTask`/`PollForDecisionTask`) backoff even when the retry token bucket is empty.\n",
