    {
      "message": "Remove the `ring` dependency from `aws-sigv4`. The `sigv4a` feature previously pulled in `ring` solely for HMAC-SHA256 in the SigV4a signing-key derivation; this is now done with the `hmac`/`sha2` (RustCrypto) crates that were already used by the SigV4 signer. `ring` is in maintenance hibernation, and the original reason for using it (a version conflict with the older `p256` crate at the time SigV4a was introduced) no longer applies. Users of the `sigv4a` feature will see `ring` removed from their dependency tree.\n",
